<div class="hero-landing clearfix">
  <%= image_tag('hero_004.jpg', alt: 'hero image') %>
  <div class="hero-text">

    <div class="hero-blurb-alt">
      <h2>Find events to paint, sip, and get artsy</h2>
      <%= link_to('Explore Art Experiences', experiences_path(month: Date.today.month), class: "btn btn-default btn-experiences right") %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="steps clearfix">
  <h1>It's easy to get started</h1>
  <div class="individual-steps col-xs-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
    <%= image_tag('step1.jpg', alt: 'first step') %>
    <p>1. Select a class</p>
    <p>Choose an available class from our class calendar.  We provide the instruction and art supplies for the class.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="individual-steps col-xs-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
    <%= image_tag('step2.jpg', alt: 'second step') %>
    <p>2. Enter the number of guests.</p>
    <p>Book the amount of tickets for the people in your party.  The more the merrier.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="individual-steps col-xs-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
    <%= image_tag('step3.jpg', alt: 'third step') %>
    <p>3. Buy drinks to enjoy during class.</p>
    <p>Purchase wine by the glass or your beverage of choice and food, at select venues. </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="experiences clearfix">
  <h1>Explore Experiences</h1>
  <%= image_tag('experience1.jpg', alt: 'experience') %>
  <%= image_tag('experience2.jpg', alt: 'experience') %>
  <%= image_tag('experience3.jpg', alt: 'experience') %>
  <%= image_tag('experience4.jpg', alt: 'experience') %>
  <%= image_tag('experience5.jpg', alt: 'experience') %>
  <div><%= link_to('See All Art Experiences', experiences_path(month: Date.today.month), class: "btn btn-default btn-experiences") %></div>
</div>
<div class="private-events clearfix">
  <div class="private-events-info col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6">
    <h1>Make It a Private Party!</h1>
    <p>Below are some of our event selections.  Submit an event request to learn more.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Birthday, bachelorette, special celebration for 15-24 guests</li>
      <li>Corporate off-site event for 25 or more guests</li>
      <li>Team building event for 15-50 guests</li>
      <li>Bachelorette wine glass painting for 15-24 guests</li>
    </ul>
    <%= link_to('Book a Private Event', new_private_event_path, class: "btn btn-default btn-experiences") %>
  </div>
  <%= image_tag('private.jpg', alt: 'private event photo', class: 'col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-6') %>
</div>
